{"tid":1727910,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"喺政府擺嘅呢個人民鬥人民嘅局，我地最大嘅武器係--持久","createTime":"2019-11-16T15:37:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-17T04:00:24.000Z","uid":264773,"like":14,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"4d0eb1e94f2313349929b648e7296990cf771eb0","tid":1727910,"uid":264773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T15:37:48.000Z","msg":"首先想講人民（深黃OR藍嘅已經冇得變，得返嘅係偏淺OR偽中立嘅一群，亦都係我想針對講嘅一群。）<br />\n如：我都支持你地，但總之唔好阻我返工<br />\n總之暴力就唔好<br />\n只睇到眼前嘅亂<br />\n<br />\n對呢班人，簡單講就係，就係要佢地失去&quot;政府而家用呢個方法去止步制亂&quot;嘅希望，<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">只要比班人見倒，點都阻止唔倒班示威者出黎整亂交通，失去用政府呢個方法去止步制亂嘅希望，一部份人自然會叫返政府讓步。</span></strong></span><br />\n有唔少人已經指出過，因為佢地最在乎只係自己利益。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">而對政府商家黎講<br />\n佢地最驚唔係你武力升級，殺警，係睇唔倒抗爭嘅終點！</span></span></strong><br />\n慢慢來自不同地方嘅壓力：中央，外國，商家，人民，甚至黑警。<br />\n所以我地唔使心急，亦唔使灰心。<br />\n我一直都覺得，一日仲有人出黎，我地就未輸。亦即係話，我地嘅輸只有一個可能性，就係冇人敢出黎OR灰心唔出黎。（都係輸比自己）<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">所以我地要繼續，唔止自己要知，仲要大大聲話比全世界知，我地嘅抗爭，永不會停，直到永遠</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n亦都係因為咁，手足一定要適當地幫自己及身邊嘅人保持冷靜，最最重要係不受傷，不被捕。<br />\n<br />\n天琦有其中一段說話： 無論係勇武定和理非，繼續做自己相信嘅野，請繼續做，我鼓勵你地去做。<br />\n<br />\n直到一天<br />\n光復香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n時代革命<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d1e31a4cea37ecfb6771112beb614d74988f870","tid":1727910,"uid":229886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T15:43:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39005cb6d6ba814f20ac994016c2710ea1beea7a","tid":1727910,"uid":229886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T15:43:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5ae42365bd22bd1feecdbf4a127266de73da775","tid":1727910,"uid":33579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T15:44:35.000Z","msg":"是<br />\n藍絲唔會咁有耐性"},{"pid":"064fe8acf8dd29c70828d9c279bce75eb908c277","tid":1727910,"uid":229886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T15:45:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14a49f8b101840c84ca99de0d19a4886ed67e41b","tid":1727910,"uid":229886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T15:45:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19eb4c44c031e0fbcb9948c053b37cb03943d009","tid":1727910,"uid":264773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T15:47:41.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"fc9f81d9f09a473156334a9960e136d1a430ea37","tid":1727910,"uid":264773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T15:51:23.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"a8cc8d65794398e942f1dd4988afe2bda1e064cf","tid":1727910,"uid":264773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T16:03:10.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"4b9cfa8